subproject.description: Electoral laws, processe and intitutions strengthen inclusive participation and professional electoral administration. subproject.description: Its specific objectives are to contribute to (1) improve electoral management capacities of EMB; to (2) consolidate lusophone Electoral Management Bodies within the Electoral Knowledge Networks and to disseminate tools and methodologies on electoral management, in Portuguese, adapted to the needs and specificities of the PALOP Timor Leste; and to (3) enhance Women and Youth’s participation and improve the capacity of parliaments and media to fulfill their role, particularly in relation to the electoral process.
